{"type": "article", "id": 18029, "title": "带水果香味的杯子", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-25T06:50:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134813Tsa5NnqmWDjotUXx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个带有水果香味的杯子，特别适合对甜水有依赖的小孩或者喜欢喝甜水但需要减肥的人。当杯子盛满水时，就能释放出对应的水果香味。他们研究发现当嗅到这些香气时，很大程度上能令人误以为喝了糖水。实际上，香气会随着使用逐渐减少，6 个月之后就会完全消散了，反过来也帮助使用者慢慢摆脱对糖分的依赖。4 种颜色的杯子分别对应柠檬、橘子、苹果、草莓这4种口味，<a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/the-right-cup-trick-your-brain-drink-more-water#/\" target=\"_blank\">目前正在众筹</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134810YSsr26jumI1Ptg5b.jpg\" width=\"618\" height=\"281\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45469256\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134811H5PuTpAochdG1anX.jpg\" width=\"620\" height=\"262\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.42258065\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134811zdle5uG2c1xCPIms.gif\" width=\"1024\" height=\"780\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76171875\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134812hFWpXS7RdDrPItwb.jpg\" width=\"620\" height=\"472\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76129032\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134812G9HlsyIxfnBdOrQh.jpg\" width=\"620\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6983871\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}